{
  "stem": "25912.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And wool was made out of tree bark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was wood wool.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I taught myself to knit, made myself a jumper and socks, then made a jumper for my mother when she came.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we, we moved into another peasant's house-- or just the two of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were strange times, because we had no money at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we were getting some food from the estate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was, drew Christmas cards, painted Christmas cards, which I sold in the village [? corp. ?] We used to go around with a pushcart, asking for brown coal for heating.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was giving French lessons, [LAUGHS] all sorts of things, because we had to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You would hear that, you know, the butcher in the village or in the nearest town had sold, had killed a pig.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So you would go there, and sometimes they would give you something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that involved going through the woods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were partisans in the woods of different groupings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In fact, in January, '45, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Biedrzycka husband and son-in-law were murdered by the Communist partisans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So life was not very easy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was quite [? a dumbhead ?] at baking bread at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we very much had to rely on ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Another source of funds was that in the ghetto, I started having some orthodontic work down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had four gold crowns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, the orthodontic work did not proceed, so the crowns were irrelevant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had them removed and sold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And gave us some-- that way, we had a bit of money to buy essentials.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then in January, the Russians arrived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Can you remember where you were when they arrived to [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were in that village, so [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They arrived.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
